<div class="container mt-5">
  <div class="jumbotron">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to WeaverBeck</h1>
    <p class="lead">Our family home in the beautiful Shuswap region of British Columbia.</p>
    <hr class="my-4">
    <p>Explore our site to learn more about our services and how we can help you achieve your goals.</p>
    <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="[% c.uri_for('/weaverbeck/about') %]" role="button">Learn More</a>
  </div>
  
  <div class="row mt-5">
    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
          <h3 class="card-title text-center">About Us</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">WeaverBeck is our family home in the beautiful Shuswap region of British Columbia. Learn more about our history, mission, and values.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer text-center">
          <a href="[% c.uri_for('/weaverbeck/about') %]" class="btn btn-primary">Read More</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">
          <h3 class="card-title text-center">Our Services</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">Discover the comprehensive range of services we offer to meet your specific needs and help you achieve your goals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer text-center">
          <a href="[% c.uri_for('/weaverbeck/services') %]" class="btn btn-success">View Services</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
          <h3 class="card-title text-center">Contact Us</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">Have questions or ready to get started? Contact us today to discuss how we can help you achieve your goals.</p>
