              </div>
              <p class="mb-1">Read about how we helped a client achieve their goals...</p>
            </a>
            <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
              <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between">
                <h5 class="mb-1">Industry Recognition</h5>
                <small>2 weeks ago</small>
              </div>
              <p class="mb-1">WeaverBeck has been recognized for excellence in...</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
